{"tid":605112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩老婆同我講 佢無得生","createTime":"2018-03-25T11:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T11:46:20.000Z","uid":31050,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4778c5db951fb9ad6215b11cad6e719df61dd624","tid":605112,"uid":31050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"佢話因為年輕時貪玩 成日同以前幾個男朋友唔用套搞 試過兩次落仔 所以醫生話已經生唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好中意小朋友 而且本身家族比較有錢同傳統 都希望生返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見佢以家不斷食補品 肥左好多 <br />\n再肥落去我真係接受唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁岩佢呢排掛住食 我攪大左屋企個靚女賓賓<br />\n諗緊同唔同佢講好"},{"pid":"2317a5e423df8e5cc723a93639d5f75e6a50377d","tid":605112,"uid":18222,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"假膠死全家"},{"pid":"4bff0cf9166ebb6f58a833740a36addc73183da8","tid":605112,"uid":155778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/605068/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/605068/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"93da4fa47c98fe2116fce90745d8d4ca0b77fd8c","tid":605112,"uid":31050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"利申 同個靚女賓妹都無用套"},{"pid":"09bebd744976594574263d8c8a2a99d24b3f2106","tid":605112,"uid":132039,"like":2,"dislike":1,"s